{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/gatsby/custom-fonts-in-gatsby-starter-bee/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"kkh913's Developer Blog","author":"[kkh913]","siteUrl":"https://kkh913.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"kkh913/utterances"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2f1d4eaa-46c9-58db-a386-f3802ec85ec7","excerpt":"This guide provides how to customize fonts for users of the gatsby-starter-bee template. üõí Font shopping Visit https://www.npmjs.com, and search for the font packages using the keyword  - for example,  and . Be sure to check the version of each font. As of the post creation date‚Ä¶","html":"<p>This guide provides how to customize fonts for users of the <a href=\"https://github.com/JaeYeopHan/gatsby-starter-bee\">gatsby-starter-bee</a> template.</p>\n<h2 id=\"üõí-font-shopping\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%F0%9F%9B%92-font-shopping\" aria-label=\"üõí font shopping permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>üõí Font shopping</h2>\n<p>Visit <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com\">https://www.npmjs.com</a>, and search for the font packages using the keyword <code class=\"language-text\">typeface-</code> - for example, <code class=\"language-text\">typeface-red-hat-display</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">typeface-red-hat-text</code>. Be sure to check the version of each font. As of the post creation date, the version of these fonts is currently <code class=\"language-text\">1.1.13</code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Ô∏è-modify-the-files\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EF%B8%8F-modify-the-files\" aria-label=\"Ô∏è modify the files permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>üñäÔ∏è Modify the files</h2>\n<h3 id=\"packagejson\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#packagejson\" aria-label=\"packagejson permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>package.json</h3>\n<p>Add the name and the version of the font packages to install the font packages.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token property\">\"dependencies\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n‚Ä¶\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"typeface-red-hat-display\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1.1.13\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"typeface-red-hat-text\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1.1.13\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"gatsby-browserjs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gatsby-browserjs\" aria-label=\"gatsby browserjs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-browser.js</h3>\n<p>Modify <code class=\"language-text\">require()</code> to use the font packages.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// custom typefaces</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// require('typeface-noto-sans-kr')</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// require('typeface-catamaran')</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'typeface-red-hat-display'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'typeface-red-hat-text'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"srccomponentstopindexscss\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#srccomponentstopindexscss\" aria-label=\"srccomponentstopindexscss permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>src/components/top/index.scss</h3>\n<p>The font of the home title.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"scss\"><pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token selector\">.link </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    ‚Ä¶\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">'Red Hat Display'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    ‚Ä¶\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"srcutilstypographyjs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#srcutilstypographyjs\" aria-label=\"srcutilstypographyjs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>src/utils/typography.js</h3>\n<p>The font of components with <code class=\"language-text\">h1</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">h2</code> tags.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">h1<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n    fontFamily<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">'Red Hat Display'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\nh2<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n    fontFamily<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">'Red Hat Display'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"srclayoutindexscss\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#srclayoutindexscss\" aria-label=\"srclayoutindexscss permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>src/layout/index.scss</h3>\n<p>The font of components with <code class=\"language-text\">body</code> tags.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"scss\"><pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token selector\">body </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">'Red Hat Text'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sans-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    ‚Ä¶\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"upgrading-npm-dependencies\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#upgrading-npm-dependencies\" aria-label=\"upgrading npm dependencies permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Upgrading npm dependencies</h2>\n<p>Please refer to <a href=\"https://www.carlrippon.com/upgrading-npm-dependencies/\">Upgrading npm dependencies</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> update <span class=\"token string\">\"typeface-red-hat-display\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"typeface-red-hat-text\"</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Custom Fonts in gatsby-starter-bee","date":"October 13, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/gatsby/custom-fonts-in-gatsby-starter-bee/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/uncategorized/start/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"start","category":"uncategorized","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/OKD/installation-guide-for-okd-3.11/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Installation Guide for OKD 3.11","category":"OKD","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","521680639"]}